column6: Data pre processing/Cleaning/ Make data ready for modelling
Separate the data wrt dependent (y) & independent (x) variables
Split this X,y data into training and testing sample (Xtrain, Xtest, Ytrain, Ytest)
Develop the model using any ML algorithm
Train the model on Xtrain & ytrain sample
Predict the values of Xtest using the trained model
Compare the Actuals (Ytest) & Predictions come from Step6
